{"tid":1921875,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"美國2019年《人權實踐報告》- 香港部分關於「功能組別」的撮要","createTime":"2020-03-12T08:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-13T02:16:01.000Z","uid":343233,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6a845b42d643c259f019c60dc0eed3892d1269","tid":1921875,"uid":343233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:39:32.000Z","msg":"基本法限制了香港人改變自己政府的能力，部份原因在於立法會至今仍未有全面普選（equal suffrage）。<br />\n<br />\n在立法會的70個議席中，只有40個由直接選舉（directly elect）產生，其餘30個由各個指定的經濟及社會界別（limited-franchise constituencies; various economic and social sectors）的約二十四萬名合資格選民選出。香港政府及建制派一直強調，功能組別的存在能將專業界別的聲音帶入議會，避免議會被民粹主義、福利主義壟斷。<br />\n<br />\n然而報告指出，功能界別的界別及其合資格選民，大多為親商界（probusiness）人士。親商界人士往往因各種考慮而支持中共政權（generally supportive of the Chinese central government），令功能組別的大部份議席落在建制派手上，<span style=\"color: red;\">可見功能組別的存在就是給予親中共人士把持立法會近半議席，防止政權受到民意或反對力量的衝擊。</span><br />\n<br />\n文件：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.state.gov/reports/2019-country-reports-on-human-rights-practices/china/hong-kong/?fbclid=IwAR2ox-oBek79UA91FZ2BSHWlB5Z3yOcKJSSVUtDEe9d1CGhpLkhslVLXK40\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.state.gov%2Freports%2F2019-country-reports-on-human-rights-practices%2Fchina%2Fhong-kong%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2ox-oBek79UA91FZ2BSHWlB5Z3yOcKJSSVUtDEe9d1CGhpLkhslVLXK40&d=2sQmvy6tOK2oFHH%2BrBh9lXG%2F0kAjhv1dd93UXbk31gU%3D&h=b3db1689\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.state.gov/reports/2019-country-reports-on-human-rights-practices/china/hong-kong/?fbclid=IwAR2ox-oBek79UA91FZ2BSHWlB5Z3yOcKJSSVUtDEe9d1CGhpLkhslVLXK40</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C1hYVnm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC1hYVnm.png&h=89fcba42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be65814e59a1a726fc69a781497b48cddaef9bbc","tid":1921875,"uid":343233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T08:44:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f804